Defendant James F Espinosa in court with attorney Jorge R Fragoso.   District Attorney's Office Law Intern appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  The Defendant was sentenced to the following:

Count #1:
IMPOSED AND STAYED SENTENCE OF:   

60 DAYS JAIL (CREDIT - 3 days if revoked);

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 YEAR (court would consider early termination of probation after 9 months based on the agents recommendation) Probation may be transferred to Milwaukee County.

